<template>

  <v-app id="inspire" >
      <v-card>
          <v-card-title>
            <btn color="Success">Nuevo Registro</btn>
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>
            <v-text-field
              v-model="search"
              label="buscar"
              mdi-search
              single-line
              hide-details
            ></v-text-field>
          </v-card-title>
      <v-data-table
        :headers="headers"
        :items="desserts"
        :search="search"
      ></v-data-table>
    </v-card>
  </v-app>

</template>



<script>
   export default {
    data : () => ({
      filters:{
        search: '',
        added_by: '',
      },
    }),
  }
</script>
